Recorded in Public Records 6/1/2022 2:14 PM OR Book 8795 Page 180,
Instrument #2022055843, Pam Childers Clerk of the Circuit Court Escambia
County, FL Recording $10,00
1MODIFICATION OF LIEN
(SHIP Housing Repair Program)
THIS MODIFICATION OF LIEN IS DATED May 31, 2022, BETWEEN Annie Bonner, (referred to
below as "Grantor"), whose address is 2025 N 11th Ave ., Pensacola, FL 32503; and ESCAMBIA COUNTY
(referred to below as "Grantee"), whose address is 221 PALAFOX PLACE, PENSACOLA, FL 32502.
LIEN. Grantor and Grantee have entered into a lien dated April 20, 2022 (the "Lien") recorded in Escambia
County, State of Florida as follows:
The Lien was recorded on 04/20/2022 Original Book 8767, page 971, Escambia County, Florida.
REAL PROPERTY DESCRIPTION. The Lien covers the following described real property (the
"Real Property") located in Escambia County, State of Florida:
N 70 FT OF LTS 6, 7, 8, 9 AND OF E 20 FT OF LT 5 BLK 3 FAIRNIE HILL PLACE PB 1 P 69 A OR
2451 P 619 CA 51.
The Real Property or its address is commonly known as 2025 N 11th Ave ., Pensacola, FL 32503
MODIFICATION. Grantor and Grantee hereby modify the Lien as follows:
The Lien referred to above is hereby modified and amended to provide that the total amount
secured by the lien increased from $16,800 to $18,200.00.
CONTINUING VALIDITY. Except as expressly modified above, the terms of the original Lien shall remain
unchanged and in full force and effect. Consent by Grantor to this Modification does not waive Grantee's
right to require strict performance of the Lien as changed above nor obligate Grantee to make any future
modifications. Nothing in this Modification shall constitute a satisfaction of the promissory note or other
credit agreement secured by the Lien (the "Note"). It is the intention of the Grantee to retain as liable all
parties to the Lien and all parties, makers and endorsers to the Note, including accommodation parties, unless
a party is expressly released by lien in writing. Any maker or endorser, including accommodation makers,
shall not be released by virtue of this Modification.
EACH GRANTOR ACKNOWLEDGES HAVING READ ALL THE PROVISIONS OF THIS
MODIFICATION OF LIEN, AND EACH GRANTOR AGREES TO ITS TERMS.
WITNESS:
LIEN:
Seamas Hunt
Annie Bonner
STATE OF FLORIDA
COUNTY OF ESCAMBIA
The foregoing instrument was acknowledged before me by means of [X] physical presence or [ ] online
notarization this_37_day of_MAL1
2022, by Annie Bonner who is personally known to me or who
has produced _FL PL
as identification and who did (did not) take an oath.
MEREDITHA. REEVES
MY COMMISSION # GG 303637
&
EXPIRES; February 26, 2023
Notary Public
Bonded Thru Notary Pubilo Underwrt
Prepared by:
Housing Department
City of Pensacola

Pensacola,FL 32521-0031
